    "The studied intra-organizational networks can be considered to be directed multiplex networks, a special type of multilayer network.",
    "Multiplex networks consist of a fixed set of nodes connected by different types of links.",
    "In our case, the G = (V, E, D) multidimensional network is associated with a multiplex network with layers G 1,.",
